<%= render 'legal_pages/legal_page_styles' %>
<div class="legal-page">
<h1>Support LexLibera</h1>

    <div class="highlight">
        <p><strong>LexLibera</strong> makes Belgian legislation and case law freely searchable with AI. The platform is run by one person &mdash; a lawyer who believes the law should not be behind a paywall. To keep this project running, we need your support.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Why your support matters</h2>
    <p>LexLibera costs money to run: server costs, AI costs for every chatbot question, storage for 185,000+ court decisions, and ongoing development of new features. Without revenue, it is impossible to keep the platform free and accessible.</p>

    <h2>&#x2B50; Subscribe to LexLibera Pro</h2>
    <p>The best way to support LexLibera is to become a <strong>Pro subscriber</strong>. For just <strong>&euro;2.99/month</strong>, you get:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>&#x2B50; Access to <strong>all intelligence levels</strong> (Genius, Mastermind, Omniscient)</li>
        <li>&#x1F4AC; <strong>15 free chatbot credits per month</strong> (for Pro subscribers)</li>
        <li>&#x1F4DC; Search <strong>parliamentary documents</strong> via the chatbot</li>
        <li>&#x1F916; Access to <strong>all AI models</strong> (GPT-5, Claude Opus 4, o4-mini, ...)</li>
    </ul>
    <% if Rails.application.config.chatbot_enabled %>
    <p><%= link_to pricing_path, class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold transition hover:opacity-90", style: "background: var(--accent-600-solid);" do %>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-amber-400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5 16L3 5l5.5 5L12 4l3.5 6L21 5l-2 11H5zm0 2h14v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H6a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1z"/></svg>
        View LexLibera Pro
    <% end %></p>
    <% end %>

    <h2>&#x2615; Donate via Ko-fi</h2>
    <p>Want to support LexLibera without a subscription? Via <strong>Ko-fi</strong>, you can make a one-time donation. Every contribution &mdash; no matter how small &mdash; helps cover server costs and keep the platform online.</p>
    <p>
        <a href="https://ko-fi.com/wetwijzerlisloi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-[#FF5E5B] hover:bg-[#e54542] text-white rounded-lg font-semibold transition">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M23.881 8.948c-.773-4.085-4.859-4.593-4.859-4.593H.723c-.604 0-.679.798-.679.798s-.082 7.324-.022 11.822c.164 2.424 2.586 2.672 2.586 2.672s8.267-.023 11.966-.049c2.438-.426 2.683-2.566 2.658-3.734 4.352.24 7.422-2.831 6.649-6.916zm-11.062 3.511c-1.246 1.453-4.011 3.976-4.011 3.976s-.121.119-.31.023c-.076-.057-.108-.09-.108-.09-.443-.441-3.368-3.049-4.034-3.954-.709-.965-1.041-2.7-.091-3.71.951-1.01 3.005-1.086 4.363.407 0 0 1.565-1.782 3.468-.963 1.904.82 1.832 3.011.723 4.311zm6.173.478c-.928.116-1.682.028-1.682.028V7.284h1.77s1.971.551 1.971 2.638c0 1.913-.985 2.667-2.059 3.015z"/></svg>
            Donate via Ko-fi
        </a>
    </p>

    <h2>&#x1F4BB; Buy Praxis</h2>
    <p><a href="https://praxislegal.be" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Praxis</a> is practice management software for Belgian lawyers: case management, client management, invoicing and AI assistant &mdash; all in one desktop application. Every Praxis subscription helps sustain the free legal information platforms (WetWijzer, LisLoi, GesetzGuide, LexLibera).</p>
    <p>
        <a href="https://praxislegal.be" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold transition hover:opacity-90" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a962, #b8943a);">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
            Discover Praxis
        </a>
    </p>

    <h2>&#x1F4E2; Spread the word</h2>
    <p>No budget? You can also support LexLibera by spreading the word:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>&#x1F517; Share <a href="https://lexlibera.be">lexlibera.be</a> with colleagues, students and friends</li>
        <li>&#x2B50; Give us a star on <a href="https://github.com/WetWijzer-LisLoi/WetWijzer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
        <li>&#x1F4AC; Mention LexLibera on social media or in professional publications</li>
        <li>&#x1F4DD; Send us your feedback at <a href="mailto:<%= contact_email %>"><%= contact_email %></a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>&#x2764;&#xFE0F; Thank you</h2>
    <p>LexLibera exists thanks to the support of our Pro subscribers, donors and users. Every contribution &mdash; financial or not &mdash; helps us keep Belgian law accessible to everyone.</p>

</div>
